{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3dbed9c0fd","title":"关于区域自治问题的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cdb4a41af0","index":0,"year":1950,"month":9,"day":16,"articleId":"3dbed9c0fd"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"f1f2bd000c","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dbed9c0fd","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。朱，指朱德。任，指任强时。李维汉，当时任中共中央统战部部长、中央人民政府民族事务委员会主任委员。"},{"id":"825cc4c259","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dbed9c0fd","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共西康区委1950年9月6日关于建立东藏自治区域人民政府问题给西南局并第十八军张国华、谭冠三等的电报。"}],"contents":[{"id":"78d0195650","type":"title","text":"关于区域自治问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dbed9c0fd"},{"id":"f1f2bd000c","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、朱、任、李维汉同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dbed9c0fd"},{"id":"825cc4c259","type":"paragraph","text":"区域自治问题，牵涉很广，有西藏、青海、宁夏、新疆、甘肃、西康、云南、广西、贵州、海南、湘西等处，有的须成立内蒙那样的大区域政府，有的须成立包括几个县的小区域政府，有的是一个县或一个区的政府，疆域划分，人员配备，政策指导，问题甚多，须加统筹。此电所称东藏自治区域，是与西康省政府并立的，还是属于西康之内的？其疆域如何？是否事前得到中央批准请维汉查告，或去电询问。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dbed9c0fd"},{"id":"8d4d13c651","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dbed9c0fd"},{"id":"6fa0fca3d1","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十六日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dbed9c0fd"}],"page":{"id":"0779f7ce18","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"3dbed9c0fd","start":161,"end":161}}}},"__N_SSG":true}